node.text:
Celebrate 10 years of BUB's Magic with her limited edition commemorative book: "Lil BUB: The Earth Years", available exclusively in the BUB STORE at the link in BUB's bio.

It's a beautiful hardbound book with over 400 pages of BUB's magic, covering her entire time on Earth, from adoption to departure. It's already more than halfway sold out, and 30% of proceeds benefit Lil BUB's Big FUND for Special Needs Pets, a 501c3 non-profit.
